(14, '{\"title\":\"Denn\\u00ed kr\\u00e9m s\\u00a0mikrofiltrovan\\u00fdm extraktem ze \\u0161ne\\u010d\\u00edho slizu, Cr\\u00e8me Supr\\u00eame\",\"id\":\"denni-krem-s-mikrofiltrovanym-extraktem-ze-sneciho-slizu-creme-supreme\",\"price\":\"1290\",\"categories\":[],\"manufacturer\":\"bioearth\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Ple\\u0165ov\\u00fd kr\\u00e9m se siln\\u00fdm tenzorov\\u00fdm efektem ur\\u010den\\u00fd k o\\u0161et\\u0159en\\u00ed poko\\u017eky vykazuj\\u00edc\\u00ed prvn\\u00ed zn\\u00e1mky st\\u00e1rnut\\u00ed.\\u00a0Obohacen\\u00fd o komplex oligopeptid\\u016f z\\u00edsk\\u00e1van\\u00fdch ze semen okra (Hibiscus aesculentus), bojuje proti tvorb\\u011b zn\\u00e1mek st\\u00e1rnut\\u00ed. M\\u00e1 stahuj\\u00edc\\u00ed \\u00fa\\u010dinky, tak\\u017ee poko\\u017eka je viditeln\\u011b hlad\\u0161\\u00ed, pevn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed a kompaktn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed.<\\/p><p><em>Funk\\u010dn\\u00ed l\\u00e1tky<\\/em><br \\/>Mikrofiltrovan\\u00fd extrakt ze \\u0161ne\\u010d\\u00edho slizu (77%), extrakt z ibi\\u0161ku, kyselina hyaluronov\\u00e1, v\\u00fdta\\u017eky z ovsa a m\\u011bs\\u00ed\\u010dku l\\u00e9ka\\u0159sk\\u00e9ho *.<\\/p><p><em>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edvat<\\/em><br \\/>Aplikujte p\\u0159\\u00edpravek na obli\\u010dej a krk r\\u00e1no a ve\\u010der lehkou kruhovou mas\\u00e1\\u017e\\u00ed.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"Biohearth\\/Denni_krem_s_mikrofiltrovanym_extraktem_ze_sneciho_slizu_Creme_Supreme.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"50 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 10:58:40\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(15, '{\"title\":\"Cleansing milk (Odli\\u010dovac\\u00ed, \\u010dist\\u00edc\\u00ed ml\\u00e9ko)\",\"id\":\"cleansing-milk-odlicovaci-cistici-mleko\",\"price\":\"410\",\"categories\":[\"physionatura-cleansing\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Uklid\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed a zvl\\u00e1\\u010d\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed produkt \\u0161etrn\\u011b a efektivn\\u011b odstra\\u0148uje make-up i r\\u016fzn\\u00e9 druhy ne\\u010distot,\\u00a0kter\\u00e9 na tv\\u00e1\\u0159i v pr\\u016fb\\u011bhu dne ulp\\u00ed.\\u00a0Respektuje p\\u0159irozenou \\u00farove\\u0148 hydratace a nenaru\\u0161uje hydrolipidov\\u00fd film k\\u016f\\u017ee. D\\u00edky unik\\u00e1tn\\u00ed receptu\\u0159e umo\\u017e\\u0148uje rychlou obnovu pleti.\\u00a0Poko\\u017eka je po pou\\u017eit\\u00ed \\u010dist\\u00e1, jemn\\u00e1 a vl\\u00e1\\u010dn\\u00e1 na dotek. Ml\\u00e9ko\\u00a0obsahuje hamamelis (Vil\\u00edn), panthenol a he\\u0159m\\u00e1nkov\\u00fd extrakt,\\u00a0kter\\u00e9 poko\\u017eku regeneruj\\u00ed, vy\\u017eivuj\\u00ed, zklid\\u0148uj\\u00ed a posiluj\\u00ed jej\\u00ed p\\u0159irozenou obranyschopnost.<\\/p><p><strong>Vhodn\\u00e9 pro:<\\/strong>\\u00a0v\\u0161echny typy pleti.<\\/p><p><strong>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edt:<\\/strong>\\u00a0naneste r\\u00e1no a ve\\u010der na ruce dostate\\u010dn\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed na navlh\\u010den\\u00fd obli\\u010dej, o\\u010dn\\u00ed kontury a krk. Krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby tv\\u00e1\\u0159 jemn\\u011b mas\\u00edrujte po dobu 30 sekund, pot\\u00e9 opl\\u00e1chn\\u011bte d\\u016fkladn\\u011b teplou vodou, osu\\u0161te a aplikujte p\\u0159\\u00edslu\\u0161n\\u00e9 pe\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00ed kroky\\u00a0Tonikum Cleansing, s\\u00e9rum a kr\\u00e9m.<\\/p><p><strong>TIP kosmeti\\u010dky:<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u010ci\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed je prvn\\u00edm a nejd\\u016fle\\u017eit\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00edm krokem v p\\u00e9\\u010di o ple\\u0165. Ml\\u00e9ko nan\\u00e1\\u0161ejte p\\u0159\\u00edmo na obli\\u010dej, nen\\u00ed zapot\\u0159eb\\u00ed pou\\u017e\\u00edvat vatov\\u00fd tamponek. Tato metoda je k pleti velmi \\u0161etrn\\u00e1 a sou\\u010dasn\\u011b efektivn\\u00ed m\\u00edsto b\\u011b\\u017en\\u00fdch vatov\\u00fdch tamponk\\u016f, kter\\u00e9 nas\\u00e1knou velk\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed produktu a poko\\u017eku m\\u016f\\u017ee n\\u00e1sledn\\u00e9 t\\u0159en\\u00ed dr\\u00e1\\u017edit. \\u010ci\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed zvy\\u0161uje \\u00fa\\u010dinek v\\u0161ech n\\u00e1sledn\\u011b pou\\u017eit\\u00fdch produkt\\u016f.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Cleansing_milk-test.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"250ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:07:30\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(16, '{\"title\":\"Bezalkoholov\\u00e9 tonikum\",\"id\":\"bezalkoholove-tonikum\",\"price\":\"410\",\"categories\":[\"physionatura-cleansing\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Tonik jde v\\u017edy ruku v\\u00a0ruce s\\u00a0odli\\u010dovac\\u00edm ml\\u00e9kem. Automaticky. V\\u017edy. Jako \\u0161amp\\u00f3n a kondicion\\u00e9r, nebo sp\\u00ed\\u0161 hrne\\u010dky a pod\\u0161\\u00e1lky, chcete-li. Pat\\u0159\\u00ed k\\u00a0sob\\u011b a jen spolu dos\\u00e1hnou k\\u00fd\\u017een\\u00e9ho efektu. Tento jemn\\u00fd tonik doslova p\\u0159et\\u00e9k\\u00e1 vysokou koncentrac\\u00ed aktivn\\u00edch v\\u00fdta\\u017ek\\u016f, <br \\/>kter\\u00e9 zp\\u016fsob\\u00ed, \\u017ee Va\\u0161e ple\\u0165 bude okouzluj\\u00edc\\u00ed.<br \\/>Obsahuje destilovanou levandulovou vodu, kter\\u00e1 ple\\u0165 hoj\\u00ed, zklid\\u0148uje a l\\u00e9\\u010d\\u00ed akn\\u00e9.\\u00a0Pomeran\\u010dov\\u00e9 kv\\u011bty, kter\\u00e9\\u00a0pom\\u00e1haj\\u00ed vyrovnat produkci mazu, sjednocuj\\u00ed t\\u00f3n pleti a rozza\\u0159ujou ji. Nav\\u00edc\\u00a0panthenol, kter\\u00fd\\u00a0zm\\u011bk\\u010duje\\u00a0ple\\u0165, zanech\\u00e1v\\u00e1 ji vyhlazenou a navrac\\u00ed jej\\u00ed p\\u0159irozenou rovnov\\u00e1hu. Tonik poko\\u017eku dokonale p\\u0159iprav\\u00ed pro aplikaci s\\u00e9ra a kr\\u00e9mu a d\\u00edky zm\\u011bk\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00edm schopnostem pom\\u016f\\u017ee dostat aktivn\\u00ed l\\u00e1tky ze s\\u00e9ra a kr\\u00e9mu je\\u0161t\\u011b hloub\\u011bji.<\\/p><p><strong>TYP PLETI:<\\/strong>\\u00a0pro v\\u0161echny typy pleti i velmi citlivou.<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Tonik p\\u0159ich\\u00e1z\\u00ed na \\u0159adu po hlavn\\u00edm \\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed pleti (ml\\u00e9ko \\/ gel \\/ p\\u011bna). Tonik naneste na vatov\\u00fd tamponek a lehce s n\\u00edm poko\\u017eku obli\\u010deje a krku osv\\u011b\\u017ete. Tonik pou\\u017eijte jak ve\\u010der, tak i samostatn\\u011b r\\u00e1no, poko\\u017eku po sp\\u00e1nku osv\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed a zbav\\u00ed vyplaven\\u00fdch toxin\\u016f, mazu a potu.<br \\/><strong>TIP KOSMETI\\u010cKY:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Tonik lze aplikovat do dlan\\u011b, rozet\\u0159\\u00edt na cel\\u00fd obli\\u010dej a dlan\\u011bmi lehce do poko\\u017eky vtla\\u010dovat, m\\u016f\\u017eete zapojit i prsty a lehce na obli\\u010dej poklep\\u00e1vat (hra na pi\\u00e1no). Nic nep\\u0159ijde nazmar a poko\\u017ece se tak dostane i lehk\\u00e9 tlakov\\u00e9 (akupresurn\\u00ed mas\\u00e1\\u017ee).<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Bezalkoholove_tonikum.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"250 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:10:58\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(17, '{\"title\":\"Satinovac\\u00ed mo\\u0159sk\\u00fd peeling na obli\\u010dej\",\"id\":\"satinovaci-morsky-peeling-na-oblicej\",\"price\":\"1300\",\"categories\":[\"physionatura-cleansing\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Siln\\u00fd exfolia\\u010dn\\u00ed peeling s\\u00a0krystaly ze soli z\\u00a0mrtv\\u00e9ho mo\\u0159e.\\u00a0Speci\\u00e1ln\\u011b vyvinut pro pot\\u0159eby sm\\u00ed\\u0161en\\u00e9, mastn\\u00e9 a problematick\\u00e9 pleti. M\\u00e1 anti-aging efekt. D\\u00edky vysok\\u00e9mu obsahu miner\\u00e1l\\u016f obnovuje bun\\u011b\\u010dn\\u00fd metabolismus a regeneruje bun\\u011b\\u010dnou strukturu poko\\u017eky. M\\u016f\\u017ee proto pomoct i v boji proti vr\\u00e1sk\\u00e1m a ztr\\u00e1t\\u011b vlhkosti v\\u00a0poko\\u017ece.\\u00a0Obsahuje esenci\\u00e1ln\\u00ed oleje ze sevilsk\\u00fdch pomeran\\u010d\\u016f, levandule, citr\\u00f3nu a tymi\\u00e1nu.\\u00a0Tyto v\\u00fdjime\\u010dn\\u00e9 slo\\u017eky maj\\u00ed\\u00a0protiz\\u00e1n\\u011btliv\\u00e9, hojiv\\u00e9 a zvlh\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00ed \\u00fa\\u010dinky.\\u00a0Poko\\u017eka je po pou\\u017eit\\u00ed jemn\\u00e1, vl\\u00e1\\u010dn\\u00e1, rozjasn\\u011bn\\u00e1 a vit\\u00e1ln\\u00ed.<\\/p><p><strong>TYP PLETI:<\\/strong>\\u00a0sm\\u00ed\\u0161en\\u00e1, mastn\\u00e1 a problematick\\u00e1 ple\\u0165, akn\\u00e9.<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Mal\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed peelingu naneste na \\u010distou a vlhkou (mokrou) poko\\u017eku obli\\u010deje, krku a dekoltu a jemn\\u00fdmi krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby mas\\u00edrujte, \\u010d\\u00edm d\\u00e9le, t\\u00edm l\\u00e9pe, alespo\\u0148 do vst\\u0159eb\\u00e1n\\u00ed materi\\u00e1lu,maxim\\u00e1ln\\u011b 8 minut. Pot\\u00e9 d\\u016fkladn\\u011b smyjte vodou a naneste pe\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00ed s\\u00e9rum a\\/nebo kr\\u00e9m. Pou\\u017e\\u00edvejte dle pot\\u0159eby, ide\\u00e1ln\\u011b 1x za 14 dn\\u00ed.<\\/p><p><strong>TIP KOSMETI\\u010cKY:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Peeling prov\\u00e1d\\u011bn\\u00fd p\\u0159ed aplikac\\u00ed ple\\u0165ov\\u00e9 masky umo\\u017e\\u0148uje aktivn\\u00edm l\\u00e1tk\\u00e1m p\\u016fsobit hloub\\u011bji a intenzivn\\u011bji. V\\u00fdsledkem bude \\u017eiv\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed, sjednocen\\u00e1 a p\\u0159irozen\\u011b nar\\u016f\\u017eov\\u011bl\\u00e1 poko\\u017eka. Nebojte se pou\\u017e\\u00edt na cel\\u00e9 t\\u011blo, v\\u010detn\\u011b podpa\\u017e\\u00ed a intimn\\u00edch parti\\u00ed (ne po depilaci).<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Satinovaci_morsky_peeling_na_oblicej.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"250g\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:16:16\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(18, '{\"title\":\"ADUEO Odli\\u010dovac\\u00ed p\\u011bna\",\"id\":\"adueo-odlicovaci-pena\",\"price\":\"720\",\"categories\":[\"physionatura-cleansing\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>\\u00da\\u010dinn\\u00fd okysli\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00ed \\u010dist\\u00edc\\u00ed ritu\\u00e1l, kter\\u00fd velmi jemn\\u011b a efektivn\\u011b odstran\\u00ed z pleti i ty nejodoln\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed ne\\u010distoty, make-up a znovu navr\\u00e1t\\u00ed pleti tolik pot\\u0159ebnou rovnov\\u00e1hu.<\\/p><p>P\\u011bna m\\u00e1 bohatou, kr\\u00e9movou a vzdu\\u0161nou konzistenci a opojnou v\\u016fni. Obsahuje\\u00a0he\\u0159m\\u00e1nkov\\u00fd extrakt, kter\\u00fd funguje skv\\u011ble nejen na zklidn\\u011bn\\u00ed mysli, ale i na ko\\u017en\\u00ed vyr\\u00e1\\u017eky, akn\\u00e9 a \\u0161patn\\u011b se hoj\\u00edc\\u00ed r\\u00e1ny. Krom\\u011b toho\\u00a0he\\u0159m\\u00e1nkov\\u00fd extrakt\\u00a0(na rozd\\u00edl od chemie a ropy) zabra\\u0148uje ucp\\u00e1v\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u00f3r\\u016f poko\\u017eky.\\u00a0Panthenol, kter\\u00fd zlep\\u0161uje stav\\u00a0pleti\\u00a0po\\u0161kozen\\u00e9 ultrafialov\\u00fdm z\\u00e1\\u0159en\\u00edm, v\\u00fdznamn\\u011b hydratuje a podporuje hojen\\u00ed, stimuluje i omlazen\\u00ed\\u00a0pleti. A olivov\\u00fd olej, kter\\u00fd hydratuje. Krom\\u011b antioxidant\\u016f obsahuje\\u00a0olivov\\u00fd olej\\u00a0i skvalen, co\\u017e je vysoce hydrata\\u010dn\\u00ed l\\u00e1tka. A v\\u00a0neposledn\\u00ed \\u0159ad\\u011b vy\\u017eivuje: Vitam\\u00edn A, D, K a E. P\\u011bna Adueo je bohat\\u00e1 na povrchov\\u011b aktivn\\u00ed l\\u00e1tky p\\u0159\\u00edrodn\\u00edho p\\u016fvodu na b\\u00e1zi cukru (bez SLS) se zklid\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00edmi vlastnostmi,\\u00a0 zvl\\u00e1\\u0161t\\u011b indikovan\\u00e1\\u00a0 pro extr\\u00e9mn\\u011b citlivou ple\\u0165.\\u00a0 Vhodn\\u00e1 i pro miminka na myt\\u00ed. P\\u011bna je tvo\\u0159ena pumpi\\u010dkou, stla\\u010den\\u00edm, nikoliv chemicky.<\\/p><p><strong>TYP PLETI:<\\/strong>\\u00a0v\\u0161echny typy pleti, doporu\\u010dujeme pro norm\\u00e1ln\\u00ed, sm\\u00ed\\u0161enou i extr\\u00e9mn\\u011b citlivou.<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Naneste p\\u011bnu na ji\\u017e navlh\\u010den\\u00fd obli\\u010dej a jemn\\u011b mas\\u00edrujte po dobu alespo\\u0148 30 sekund. Mas\\u00e1\\u017e\\u00ed dojde k uvoln\\u011bn\\u00ed ne\\u010distot a z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 se podpo\\u0159\\u00ed mikrocirkulace (prokrven\\u00ed). Pou\\u017eijte r\\u00e1no a \\/ nebo ve\\u010der. D\\u016fkladn\\u011b opl\\u00e1chn\\u011bte a pokra\\u010dujte v b\\u011b\\u017en\\u00e9 rutinn\\u00ed p\\u00e9\\u010di o ple\\u0165 (tonikum, s\\u00e9rum a kr\\u00e9m).<\\/p><p><strong>TIP:<\\/strong>\\u00a0ide\\u00e1ln\\u00ed do sprchy<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/ADUEO_Odlicovaci_pena.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"150 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:18:34\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(19, '{\"title\":\"Peeling z\\u00a0meru\\u0148kov\\u00fdch jadrer \",\"id\":\"peeling-z-merunkovych-jadrer\",\"price\":\"680\",\"categories\":[\"starway\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Tento ml\\u00e9\\u010dn\\u00fd ple\\u0165ov\\u00fd peeling obsahuje mikro \\u010d\\u00e1ste\\u010dky z meru\\u0148kov\\u00fdch jader, kter\\u00e9 jemn\\u011b odstra\\u0148uj\\u00ed odum\\u0159el\\u00e9 ko\\u017en\\u00ed bu\\u0148ky a ne\\u010distoty. Ple\\u0165 \\u010dist\\u00ed, zjem\\u0148uje a vyhlazuje.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><strong>TYP PLETI:<\\/strong>\\u00a0v\\u0161echny typy pleti.<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0mal\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed peelingu naneste na vlhkou a \\u010distou poko\\u017eku obli\\u010deje, krku a dekoltu a jemn\\u00fdmi krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby mas\\u00edrujte. Pot\\u00e9 d\\u016fkladn\\u011b smyjte a naneste pe\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00ed s\\u00e9rum a\\/nebo kr\\u00e9m.\\u00a0Pou\\u017e\\u00edvejte podle pot\\u0159eby 1x za 14 dn\\u00ed.<\\/p><p><strong>TIP KOSMETI\\u010cKY:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Expres kosmetick\\u00e9 o\\u0161et\\u0159en\\u00ed. Naneste peeling ve\\u010der na vlhkou a \\u010distou poko\\u017eku obli\\u010deje, krku a dekoltu a jemn\\u00fdmi krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby mas\\u00edrujte. Pot\\u00e9 d\\u016fkladn\\u011b smyjte a naneste pe\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00ed masku, masku nechte p\\u016fsobit 10 minut, pot\\u00e9 d\\u016fkladn\\u011b smyjte a naneste s\\u00e9rum a\\/nebo kr\\u00e9m. Va\\u0161\\u00ed pleti se tak dostane jedine\\u010dn\\u00e9 p\\u00e9\\u010de jako v kosmetick\\u00e9m sal\\u00f3nu a po probuzen\\u00ed bude jako znovu zrozen\\u00e1.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Peeling_z_merunkovych_jadrer.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"500 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:20:26\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(20, '{\"title\":\"Arganovo - mandlov\\u00fd mas\\u00e1\\u017en\\u00ed olej\",\"id\":\"arganovo-mandlovy-masazni-olej\",\"price\":\"680\",\"categories\":[\"starway\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Bohat\\u00fd \\u00a0mas\\u00e1\\u017en\\u00ed olej s nenasycen\\u00fdmi mastn\\u00fdmi kyselinami, kter\\u00e9 jsou d\\u016fle\\u017eit\\u00e9 pro obnovu a regeneraci poko\\u017eky. Obsahuje arganov\\u00fd olej, kter\\u00fd zbavuje poko\\u017eku p\\u0159ebyte\\u010dn\\u00e9ho mazu, zpomaluje tvorbu vr\\u00e1sek a chr\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u0159ed vlivy prost\\u0159ed\\u00ed a \\u010dasu. Poko\\u017eku nemast\\u00ed, ale zanech\\u00e1v\\u00e1 hebkou a vl\\u00e1\\u010dnou.\\u00a0 Mandlov\\u00fd olej\\u00a0se \\u0159ad\\u00ed mezi nejcenn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed rostlinn\\u00e9 oleje. Je v\\u00fd\\u017eivn\\u00fd a vhodn\\u00fd pro v\\u0161echny typy\\u00a0pleti. Poko\\u017ece dod\\u00e1v\\u00e1 pocit hebkosti, m\\u00edrn\\u00ed podr\\u00e1\\u017ed\\u011bn\\u00ed, chr\\u00e1n\\u00ed ji a pom\\u00e1h\\u00e1 p\\u0159edev\\u0161\\u00edm such\\u00e9 k\\u016f\\u017ei se sklony k olupov\\u00e1n\\u00ed, sv\\u011bd\\u011bn\\u00ed a poprask\\u00e1n\\u00ed. Slune\\u010dnicov\\u00fd olej, kter\\u00fd m\\u00e1 zvl\\u00e1\\u010d\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed\\u00a0\\u00fa\\u010dinky, d\\u00edky vysok\\u00e9mu obsahu vitaminu E k\\u016f\\u017ei v\\u00fdborn\\u011b hoj\\u00ed a regeneruje. <br \\/><strong>TYP PLETI:<\\/strong>\\u00a0v\\u0161echny typy pleti.<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0mal\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed oleje naneste na \\u010distou poko\\u017eku obli\\u010deje, krku a dekoltu a jemn\\u00fdmi krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby mas\\u00edrujte.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Arganovo_-_mandlovy_masazni_olej.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"500 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:21:40\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}');
