(21, '{\"title\":\"Kr\\u00e9m na such\\u00e9 ruce\",\"id\":\"krem-na-suche-ruce\",\"price\":\"680\",\"categories\":[\"starway\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Speci\\u00e1ln\\u011b vyvinut\\u00fd kr\\u00e9m pro udr\\u017een\\u00ed mlad\\u00e9 a kr\\u00e1sn\\u00e9 poko\\u017eky rukou\\u00a0bez pocitu mastnoty. Obsahuje\\u00a0olivov\\u00fd olej, kter\\u00fd hydratuje a udr\\u017euje poko\\u017eku vl\\u00e1\\u010dnou a jemnou. D\\u00e1le\\u00a0citronovou \\u0161\\u0165\\u00e1vu, vytam\\u00edn E\\u00a0a\\u00a0panthenol, kter\\u00e9 udr\\u017euj\\u00ed ruce revitalizovan\\u00e9, vl\\u00e1\\u010dn\\u00e9 a regeneruj\\u00ed nam\\u00e1hanou poko\\u017eku rukou.\\u00a0 Kr\\u00e9m je tak\\u00e9 ide\\u00e1ln\\u00ed jako p\\u00e9\\u010de o nehty a nehtovou k\\u016f\\u017ei\\u010dku.<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0aplikujte mal\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed kr\\u00e9mu na h\\u0159bet ruky a lehce o sebe vmas\\u00edrujte do poko\\u017eky rukou. Pou\\u017eijte kdykoli b\\u011bhem dne dle pot\\u0159eby, nebo po ka\\u017ed\\u00e9m umyt\\u00ed.<\\/p><p><strong>TIP KOSMETI\\u010cKY:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Wellness pro Va\\u0161e ruce \\u2013 ruce omyjte, osu\\u0161te, aplikujte mal\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed t\\u011blov\\u00e9ho peelingu a po dobu n\\u011bkolika minut mas\\u00edrujte poko\\u017eku rukou. Peeling jemn\\u011b odstran\\u00ed odum\\u0159el\\u00e9 bu\\u0148ky k\\u016f\\u017ee, obnov\\u00ed, zjemn\\u00ed a vyhlad\\u00ed. Pot\\u00e9 smyjte, na je\\u0161t\\u011b vlhk\\u00e9 ruce naneste 3 kapky\\u00a0arganovo-mandlov\\u00e9ho oleje\\u00a0Starway, vmas\\u00edrujte. V\\u011bnujte pozornost neht\\u016fm i nehtov\\u00e9 k\\u016f\\u017ei\\u010dce, olej se kr\\u00e1sn\\u011b vst\\u0159eb\\u00e1. Na z\\u00e1v\\u011br naneste kr\\u00e9m na ruce. Va\\u0161e ruce budou vy\\u017eiven\\u00e9, kr\\u00e1sn\\u00e9 a hebk\\u00e9.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Krem_na_suche_ruce.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"500 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:23:21\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(22, '{\"title\":\"Odli\\u010dovac\\u00ed ml\\u00e9ko s\\u00a0panthenolem\",\"id\":\"odlicovaci-mleko-s-panthenolem\",\"price\":\"680\",\"categories\":[\"starway\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Toto bohat\\u00e9 ml\\u00e9ko d\\u016fkladn\\u011b poko\\u017eku \\u010dist\\u00ed, zanech\\u00e1v\\u00e1 ji hladkou, \\u010distou, hydratovanou a navozuje tak pocit dokonal\\u00e9ho zklidn\\u011bn\\u00ed a sv\\u011b\\u017eesti.<\\/p><p>D\\u00edky slune\\u010dnicov\\u00e9mu oleji\\u00a0hydratuje, vy\\u017eivuje, posiluje a m\\u00e1 anti-agingov\\u00e9 a antioxida\\u010dn\\u00ed \\u00fa\\u010dinky. Extrakt z\\u00a0he\\u0159m\\u00e1nku m\\u00e1 neoby\\u010dejn\\u00e9 zklid\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed a revitaliza\\u010dn\\u00ed \\u00fa\\u010dinky, je tak\\u00e9 cen\\u011bn\\u00fd pro sv\\u00e9 protiz\\u00e1n\\u011btliv\\u00e9, protialergenn\\u00ed \\u00fa\\u010dinky, nav\\u00edc je analgetick\\u00fd a hojiv\\u00fd. Obsa\\u017een\\u00e1 \\u0161\\u0165\\u00e1va z\\u00a0Aloe vera\\u00a0pom\\u00e1h\\u00e1 v poko\\u017ece udr\\u017eet pot\\u0159ebnou hydrataci, d\\u00edky \\u010demu\\u017e ji chr\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u0159ed vysu\\u0161en\\u00edm a pocitem pnut\\u00ed.<\\/p><p><strong>TYP PLETI:<\\/strong>\\u00a0pro v\\u0161echny typy pleti, vhodn\\u00e1 pro unavenou a zralou.<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Aplikujte dostate\\u010dn\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed na obli\\u010dej, o\\u010dn\\u00ed kontury a krk. Krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby poko\\u017eku jemn\\u011b mas\\u00edrujte. Prov\\u00e1d\\u011bjte \\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed alespo\\u0148 30 sekund, pot\\u00e9 smyjte d\\u016fkladn\\u011b vodou a osu\\u0161te.<\\/p><p><strong>TIP KOSMETI\\u010cKY:<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u010ci\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed je prvn\\u00edm a nejd\\u016fle\\u017eit\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00edm krokem v p\\u00e9\\u010di o ple\\u0165. Jen \\u010dist\\u00e1 ple\\u0165 je zdrav\\u00e1 a kr\\u00e1sn\\u00e1. Ml\\u00e9ko nan\\u00e1\\u0161ejte p\