(23, '{\"title\":\"Tonikum s\\u00a0levandul\\u00ed\",\"id\":\"tonikum-s-levanduli\",\"price\":\"680\",\"categories\":[\"starway\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Tento jemn\\u00fd tonik doslova p\\u0159et\\u00e9k\\u00e1 vysokou koncentrac\\u00ed aktivn\\u00edch v\\u00fdta\\u017ek\\u016f, kter\\u00e9 zp\\u016fsob\\u00ed, \\u017ee Va\\u0161e ple\\u0165 bude okouzluj\\u00edc\\u00ed.<\\/p><p>Obsahuje kv\\u011btinov\\u00e9 extrakty z levandule, kter\\u00e1 podporuje regeneraci poko\\u017eky, m\\u00e1 dezinfek\\u010dn\\u00ed a antibakteri\\u00e1ln\\u00ed\\u00a0\\u00fa\\u010dinky, zklid\\u0148uje a uvol\\u0148uje nap\\u011bt\\u00ed.<br \\/>V\\u00fdta\\u017eek hamamelis, Vil\\u00edn\\u00a0je nesm\\u00edrn\\u011b obl\\u00edben\\u00e1 ingredience v produktech p\\u00e9\\u010de o\\u00a0ple\\u0165, zejm\\u00e9na d\\u00edky sv\\u00fdm stahuj\\u00edc\\u00edm a toniza\\u010dn\\u00edm\\u00a0\\u00fa\\u010dink\\u016fm.\\u00a0Nav\\u00edc\\u00a0extrakt z\\u00a0medu udr\\u017euje\\u00a0ple\\u0165\\u00a0hydratovanou, reguluje pH poko\\u017eky a chr\\u00e1n\\u00ed bu\\u0148ky p\\u0159ed po\\u0161kozen\\u00edm.<br \\/>Urea udr\\u017euje vyrovnan\\u00e9 pH poko\\u017eky a napom\\u00e1h\\u00e1 pronik\\u00e1n\\u00ed dal\\u0161\\u00edch \\u00fa\\u010dinn\\u00fdch l\\u00e1tek hluboko do poko\\u017eky. V\\u00e1\\u017ee na sebe velk\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed vody a hydratuje\\u00a0ple\\u0165\\u00a0do hloubky bez zbyte\\u010dn\\u00e9ho zat\\u00ed\\u017een\\u00ed. Nav\\u00edc kys. ml\\u00e9\\u010dn\\u00e1 a citr\\u00f3nov\\u00e1 ple\\u0165 osv\\u011b\\u017euj\\u00ed, posiluj\\u00ed a zachov\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed elasticitu.<br \\/>Tonik poko\\u017eku dokonale p\\u0159iprav\\u00ed pro aplikaci s\\u00e9ra a kr\\u00e9mu a d\\u00edky zm\\u011bk\\u010duj\\u00edc\\u00edm schopnostem pom\\u016f\\u017ee dostat aktivn\\u00ed l\\u00e1tky ze s\\u00e9ra a kr\\u00e9mu je\\u0161t\\u011b hloub\\u011bji.<\\/p><p><strong>TYP PLETI:<\\/strong>\\u00a0pro v\\u0161echny typy pleti i velmi citlivou<\\/p><p><strong>JAK POU\\u017d\\u00cdT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Tonik p\\u0159ich\\u00e1z\\u00ed na \\u0159adu po hlavn\\u00edm \\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed pleti (ml\\u00e9ko \\/ gel \\/ p\\u011bna). Tonik naneste na vatov\\u00fd tamponek a lehce s n\\u00edm poko\\u017eku obli\\u010deje a krku osv\\u011b\\u017ete. Tonik pou\\u017eijte jak ve\\u010der, tak i samostatn\\u011b r\\u00e1no, poko\\u017eku po sp\\u00e1nku osv\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed a zbav\\u00ed vyplaven\\u00fdch toxin\\u016f, mazu a potu.<\\/p><p><strong>TIP KOSMETI\\u010cKY:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Tonik lze aplikovat do dlan\\u011b, rozet\\u0159\\u00edt na cel\\u00fd obli\\u010dej a dlan\\u011bmi lehce do poko\\u017eky vtla\\u010dovat, m\\u016f\\u017eete zapojit i prsty a lehce na obli\\u010dej poklep\\u00e1vat (hra na pi\\u00e1no). Nic nep\\u0159ijde nazmar a poko\\u017ece se tak dostane i lehk\\u00e9 tlakov\\u00e9 (akupresurn\\u00ed mas\\u00e1\\u017ee).<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Tonikum_s_levanduli.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"500 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:25:53\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(24, '{\"title\":\"Hydrata\\u010dn\\u00ed maska\",\"id\":\"hydratacni-maska\",\"price\":\"680\",\"categories\":[\"armonia\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>\\u010cist\\u00edc\\u00ed ple\\u0165ov\\u00e1 maska s j\\u00edlem, hamamelis a panthenolem hloubkov\\u011b \\u010dist\\u00ed a obnovuje ple\\u0165. Absorbuje p\\u0159ebyte\\u010dn\\u00fd maz a zjem\\u0148uje celkovou texturu pleti. Po pou\\u017eit\\u00ed okam\\u017eit\\u011b vid\\u00edte, \\u017ee je ple\\u0165 projasn\\u011bn\\u00e1, \\u010dist\\u00e1, jemn\\u00e1 a vl\\u00e1\\u010dn\\u00e1.\\u00a0Obsahuje \\u00fa\\u017easn\\u00e9 \\u010dist\\u00edc\\u00ed, hojiv\\u00e9 a obnovuj\\u00edc\\u00ed l\\u00e1tky.<\\/p><p><strong>Vhodn\\u00e1 pro:<\\/strong>\\u00a0norm\\u00e1ln\\u00ed, sm\\u00ed\\u0161en\\u00e1, mastn\\u00e1 a hrub\\u00e1 ple\\u0165, akn\\u00e9, ucpan\\u00e9 p\\u00f3ry, nadm\\u011brn\\u00fd lesk.<\\/p><p><strong>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edt:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Naneste na \\u010distou tv\\u00e1\\u0159,\\u00a0nechte p\\u016fsobit jen alespo\\u0148 8 minut. Pot\\u00e9 d\\u016fkladn\\u011b opl\\u00e1chn\\u011bte vodou. Na z\\u00e1v\\u011br naneste s\\u00e9rum a lehk\\u00fd hydrata\\u010dn\\u00ed kr\\u00e9m.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Hydratacni_maska.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"125 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:27:37\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
