(27, '{\"title\":\"S\\u00e9rum s\\u00a0vit.C\",\"id\":\"serum-s-vit-c\",\"price\":\"900\",\"categories\":[\"energheia\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Vitam\\u00edn C je z\\u00e1kladn\\u00ed prvek pro lidsk\\u00e9 zdrav\\u00ed, \\u0161iroce vyu\\u017e\\u00edvan\\u00fd v kosmetice pro sv\\u00e9 v\\u00fdjime\\u010dn\\u00e9 omlazuj\\u00edc\\u00ed a projas\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed vlastnosti. Chr\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u0159ed p\\u0159ed\\u010dasn\\u00fdm st\\u00e1rnut\\u00edm, p\\u0159ed voln\\u00fdmi radik\\u00e1ly, stimuluje tvorbu kolagenu a osv\\u011bd\\u010dil se na projasn\\u011bn\\u00ed a eliminaci tmav\\u00fdch skvrn (pigmentov\\u00e9, sta\\u0159eck\\u00e9).<\\/p><p><strong>Vhodn\\u00fd pro:<\\/strong>\\u00a0unaven\\u00e1 ple\\u0165 bez jasu, vr\\u00e1sky, pigmentov\\u00e9 skvrny, barevn\\u011b nejednotn\\u00e1 ple\\u0165.<\\/p><p><strong>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edt:<\\/strong>\\u00a0naneste 2 a\\u017e 3 kapky na celou tv\\u00e1\\u0159 v\\u010detn\\u011b oblasti o\\u010dn\\u00edho okol\\u00ed\\/o\\u010dn\\u00edch kontur, vyhn\\u011bte se p\\u0159\\u00edm\\u00e9mu kontaktu s o\\u010dima.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><strong>Upozorn\\u011bn\\u00ed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0vyvarujte se p\\u0159\\u00edm\\u00e9mu m\\u00edch\\u00e1n\\u00ed s KYSELINOU GLYKOLOVOU 10% nebo oba produkty pou\\u017e\\u00edvejte odd\\u011blen\\u011b. Pokud pou\\u017eijete tak\\u00e9 ZINEK + NIACINAMID 11% a PEPTIDY + IBI\\u0160EK 2%, v\\u017edy a\\u017e po VITAMINU C, ale ne sm\\u00edchan\\u00e9 dohromady.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Serum_s_vit_C.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"30ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:34:04\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(28, '{\"title\":\"Jemn\\u00fd odli\\u010dova\\u010d o\\u010d\\u00ed\",\"id\":\"jemny-odlicovac-oci\",\"price\":\"480\",\"categories\":null,\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Delik\\u00e1tn\\u00ed o\\u010dn\\u00ed odli\\u010dova\\u010d, pro jemn\\u00e9 a citliv\\u00e9 oblasti okolo o\\u010d\\u00ed. Pom\\u00e1h\\u00e1 sni\\u017eovat zarudnut\\u00ed po odl\\u00ed\\u010den\\u00ed a zanech\\u00e1v\\u00e1 poko\\u017eku sv\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed a odpo\\u010datou. Obsahuje bisabolol (hlavn\\u00ed slo\\u017eka silice z he\\u0159m\\u00e1nku l\\u00e9ka\\u0159sk\\u00e9ho), kter\\u00fd m\\u00e1 siln\\u00e9 protiz\\u00e1n\\u011btliv\\u00e9 a antimikrobi\\u00e1ln\\u00ed vlastnosti.\\u00a0 100% \\u00fa\\u010dinky uvid\\u00edme tedy na pleti z\\u00e1n\\u011btliv\\u00e9, mast\\u00edc\\u00ed se, a\\u017e akn\\u00f3zn\\u00ed. Ple\\u0165 uklid\\u0148uje a regeneruje. Vhodn\\u00fd je tak\\u00e9 pro popraskan\\u00e9 rty, ruce nebo chodidla. V kosmetice zlep\\u0161\\u00ed vst\\u0159ebatelnost dal\\u0161\\u00edch l\\u00e1tek. Poko\\u017eku vyhlazuje a dod\\u00e1 j\\u00ed jemnost.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Jemny_odlicovac_oci_200ml.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"20 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:35:50\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(29, '{\"title\":\"Lactica AHA \\u010dist\\u00edc\\u00ed gel\",\"id\":\"lactica-aha-cistici-gel\",\"price\":\"760\",\"categories\":[\"lactica\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Speci\\u00e1ln\\u00ed\\u00a0jemn\\u00fd \\u010dist\\u00edc\\u00ed gel, s\\u00a0pH 3,5 \\u0161etrn\\u011b a efektivn\\u011b \\u010dist\\u00ed ka\\u017edodenn\\u00ed ne\\u010distoty, v\\u010detn\\u011b make-upu. Kysel\\u00e9 pH zajist\\u00ed, \\u017ee p\\u0159i \\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed nedojde k naru\\u0161en\\u00ed ochrann\\u00e9ho filmu poko\\u017eky, respektuje jej\\u00ed kysel\\u00fd pl\\u00e1\\u0161\\u0165. Perfektn\\u00ed pro pou\\u017eit\\u00ed samostatn\\u011b nebo jako druh\\u00fd krok p\\u0159i dvojit\\u00e9m \\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed. Po pou\\u017eit\\u00ed je ple\\u0165 \\u010dist\\u00e1, vl\\u00e1\\u010dn\\u00e1, hebk\\u00e1 na dotek.\\u00a0Obsahuje\\u00a0p\\u0159\\u00edrodn\\u00ed zklid\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed a hojiv\\u00e9 l\\u00e1tky:\\u00a0extrakt z\\u00a0he\\u0159m\\u00e1nku a panthenol. Kyselinu mandlovou, ml\\u00e9\\u010dnou a glykolovou.<\\/p><p><strong>Vhodn\\u00fd pro:<\\/strong>\\u00a0norm\\u00e1ln\\u00ed, sm\\u00ed\\u0161en\\u00e1, mastn\\u00e1 ple\\u0165, ucpan\\u00e9 p\\u00f3ry, akn\\u00e9, nadm\\u011brn\\u00fd lesk.<\\/p><p><strong>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edt:\\u00a0<\\/strong>Tv\\u00e1\\u0159 navlh\\u010dete vodou, 1 a\\u017e 2 pumpi\\u010dky gelu naneste na tv\\u00e1\\u0159 a prove\\u010fte jemnou mas\\u00e1\\u017e krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby. Mas\\u00e1\\u017e\\u00ed dojde k uvoln\\u011bn\\u00ed ne\\u010distot, ple\\u0165 se hezky prokrv\\u00ed a podpo\\u0159\\u00ed se mikrocirkulace. Pot\\u00e9 d\\u016fkladn\\u011b opl\\u00e1chn\\u011bte vodou. V p\\u0159\\u00edpad\\u011b velk\\u00e9ho l\\u00ed\\u010den\\u00ed prove\\u010fte tento proces 2x. Na z\\u00e1v\\u011br naneste tonikum, s\\u00e9rum a kr\\u00e9m, u mlad\\u00e9 pleti posta\\u010d\\u00ed pouze kr\\u00e9m.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\