(30, '{\"title\":\"Lactica AHA gel maska\",\"id\":\"lactica-aha-gel-maska\",\"price\":\"1000\",\"categories\":[\"lactica\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Alfa-hydroxy\\u00a0kyseliny, nebo-li ovocn\\u00e9 peelingy,\\u00a0nejsou v\\u00a0kosmetick\\u00e9 p\\u00e9\\u010di nic nov\\u00e9ho. U\\u017e Kleopatra se koupala v\\u00a0ml\\u00e9ce \\/kyselina ml\\u00e9\\u010dn\\u00e1\\/, \\u0158ekov\\u00e9 o\\u0161et\\u0159ovali pop\\u00e1leniny \\u010derven\\u00fdm v\\u00ednem\\/kyselina vinn\\u00e1\\/ a pigmentov\\u00e9 skvrny si\\u00a0odstra\\u0148ovali citr\\u00f3nem\\/kyselina citronov\\u00e1\\/. Tyto ovocn\\u00e9 kyseliny obsa\\u017een\\u00e9 v\\u00a0\\u0159ad\\u011b LACTICA byly vyvinuty\\u00a0tak, aby umo\\u017e\\u0148ovaly povrchovou exfoliaci poko\\u017eky, tzn. odstra\\u0148ovaly odum\\u0159el\\u00e9 bu\\u0148ky a z\\u00e1rove\\u0148\\u00a0stimulovaly bun\\u011b\\u010dn\\u00e9 omlazen\\u00ed a obnovily pH poko\\u017eky tak, aby byla zdrav\\u00e1 a z\\u00e1\\u0159iv\\u00e1.<\\/p><p><strong>Vhodn\\u00fd pro:<\\/strong>\\u00a0norm\\u00e1ln\\u00ed, sm\\u00ed\\u0161en\\u00e1, mastn\\u00e1 ple\\u0165, ucpan\\u00e9 p\\u00f3ry, akn\\u00e9, nadm\\u011brn\\u00fd lesk.<\\/p><p><strong>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edt:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Naneste masku ve v\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed vrstv\\u011b a nechejte p\\u016fsobit asi 10\\/15 minut. Odstra\\u0148te zbytky\\u00a0pomoc\\u00ed houbi\\u010dek a vla\\u017en\\u00e9 vody a pot\\u00e9 pokra\\u010dujte v\\u00a0o\\u0161et\\u0159en\\u00ed nanesen\\u00edm kysel\\u00e9ho kr\\u00e9mu.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Lactica_AHA_gel_maska.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"250 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:38:58\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(31, '{\"title\":\"Lactica AHA kysel\\u00fd kr\\u00e9m\",\"id\":\"lactica-aha-kysely-krem\",\"price\":\"820\",\"categories\":[\"lactica\"],\"manufacturer\":\"physio-natura\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Kysel\\u00fd kr\\u00e9m ur\\u010den\\u00fd k\\u00a0podpo\\u0159e hloubkov\\u00e9ho exfolia\\u010dn\\u00edho \\u00fa\\u010dinku pomoc\\u00ed\\u00a0AHA kyselin. P\\u0159i respektov\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u0159irozen\\u00e9 \\u00farovn\\u011b kyselosti pleti\\u00a0stimuluje tento kr\\u00e9m tvorbu\\u00a0nov\\u00fdch ko\\u017en\\u00edch bun\\u011bk, co\\u017e je velmi \\u00fa\\u010dinn\\u00e9 p\\u0159i prevenci tvorby vr\\u00e1sek i akn\\u00e9.<\\/p><p><strong>Vhodn\\u00fd pro:<\\/strong>\\u00a0pro v\\u0161echny typy plet\\u00ed trp\\u00edc\\u00ed suchost\\u00ed a\\u017e \\u0161upinat\\u011bn\\u00edm, dehydratac\\u00ed a \\u00a0tak\\u00e9 pro ple\\u0165 s\\u00a0rosaceou.<\\/p><p><strong>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edt:\\u00a0<\\/strong>Aplikujte v\\u00fdrobek po pe\\u010dliv\\u00e9m \\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed. Jemn\\u011b mas\\u00edrujte krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby, dokud se v\\u00fdrobek zcela nevst\\u0159eb\\u00e1.<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"PhysioNatura\\/Lactica_AHA_kysely_krem.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"50 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 13:40:59\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
(32, '{\"title\":\"Detoxika\\u010dn\\u00ed jemn\\u00fd kr\\u00e9m na kontury o\\u010d\\u00ed\",\"id\":\"detoxikacni-jemny-krem-na-kontury-oci\",\"price\":\"690\",\"categories\":[],\"manufacturer\":\"naobay\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>Ultra \\u010derstv\\u00e1 a \\u00fa\\u010dinn\\u00e1 sm\\u011bs p\\u0159\\u00edsad, kter\\u00e9 omlad\\u00ed v\\u00e1\\u0161 obli\\u010dej a probud\\u00ed va\\u0161e o\\u010di.\\u00a0Antioxida\\u010dn\\u00ed prysky\\u0159ice dra\\u010d\\u00edho stromu se kombinuje s dekongestivn\\u00edm kofeinem k prevenci a oprav\\u011b st\\u00e1rnut\\u00ed poko\\u017eky.\\u00a0V jemn\\u00e9 kontu\\u0159e o\\u010d\\u00ed naprav\\u00ed unaven\\u00fd v\\u00fdraz.\\u00a0Receptura tak\\u00e9 obsahuje \\u00fa\\u010dinnou \\u010dervenou mo\\u0159skou \\u0159asu a aktivn\\u00ed slo\\u017eku Chilean Tara, kter\\u00e1 bude m\\u00edt okam\\u017eit\\u00fd liftingov\\u00fd efekt.\\u00a0Rovn\\u011b\\u017e obsahuje kyselinu hyaluronovou, skv\\u011bl\\u00fd zvlh\\u010dova\\u010d, kter\\u00fd tak\\u00e9 chr\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u0159ed voln\\u00fdmi radik\\u00e1ly a zvy\\u0161uje koncentraci vnit\\u0159n\\u00edho kolagenu.<br \\/>Vhodn\\u00fd pro v\\u0161echny typy vzhled\\u016f a k pou\\u017eit\\u00ed na cel\\u00fd obli\\u010dej, zvl\\u00e1\\u0161t\\u011b pokud je va\\u0161e poko\\u017eka citliv\\u00e1 nebo chcete extra antioxida\\u010dn\\u00ed p\\u00e9\\u010di.<\\/p><p><em>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edvat<\\/em><br \\/>Naneste r\\u00e1no a ve\\u010der na o\\u010dn\\u00ed okol\\u00ed jemn\\u00fdmi dotyky a dokon\\u010dete krou\\u017eiv\\u00fdmi pohyby pro \\u00fapln\\u00e9 vst\\u0159eb\\u00e1n\\u00ed.\\u00a0Lze pou\\u017e\\u00edt na cel\\u00fd obli\\u010dej.<\\/p><p><em>Ingredience<\\/em><br \\/>Aqua,\\u00a0Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice*,\\u00a0Caprylic\\/capric triglyceride,\\u00a0Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-6 Distearate,\\u00a0Cetyl Alcohol,\\u00a0Vitis vinifera seed oil*,\\u00a0Coco-Caprylate\\/Caprate, Distarch Phosphate,\\u00a0PRUNUS ARMENIACA KERNEL OIL*,\\u