(37, '{\"title\":\"\\u010cist\\u00edc\\u00ed ple\\u0165ov\\u00e9 ml\\u00e9ko ORIGIN\",\"id\":\"cistici-pletove-mleko-origin\",\"price\":\"590\",\"categories\":[],\"manufacturer\":\"naobay\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>\\u010cistic\\u00ed ple\\u0165ov\\u00e9 ml\\u00e9ko, kter\\u00e9 hloubkov\\u011b vy\\u010dist\\u00ed va\\u0161i poko\\u017eku a zanech\\u00e1 ji jemnou, \\u010distou a hydratovanou d\\u00edky \\u010distic\\u00edm olej\\u016fm, jako je d\\u00fd\\u0148ov\\u00fd olej *, olivov\\u00fd olej *, tyg\\u0159\\u00ed o\\u0159ech *a r\\u00fd\\u017eov\\u00fd olej *, kter\\u00e9 poskytuj\\u00ed vlastnosti proti st\\u00e1rnut\\u00ed a antioxida\\u010dn\\u00ed vlastnosti.<\\/p><p>Toto \\u010distic\\u00ed ml\\u00e9ko m\\u00eds\\u00ed zklid\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed a uklid\\u0148uj\\u00edc\\u00ed vlastnosti extraktu z organick\\u00e9 Violet * s hydrata\\u010dn\\u00edm a antioxida\\u010dn\\u00edm p\\u016fsoben\\u00edm v\\u00fdta\\u017ek\\u016f z Apple * a Lemon *.\\u00a0Obsahuje tak\\u00e9 pomeran\\u010dovou kv\\u011btovou vodu *, kter\\u00e1 dod\\u00e1v\\u00e1 jemnost a sv\\u011b\\u017eest.<\\/p><p><em>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edvat<\\/em><\\/p><p><strong>TIP KOSMETI\\u010cKY:\\u00a0<\\/strong><br \\/>Ml\\u00e9ko nan\\u00e1\\u0161ejte na navlh\\u010den\\u00e9 ruce, nen\\u00ed zapot\\u0159eb\\u00ed pou\\u017e\\u00edvat vatov\\u00fd tamponek.<br \\/>Ten vs\\u00e1kne a spot\\u0159ebuje velk\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed ml\\u00e9ka, nav\\u00edc m\\u016f\\u017ee t\\u0159en\\u00ed tamponkem dr\\u00e1\\u017edit obli\\u010dej a celkov\\u011b m\\u016f\\u017ee b\\u00fdt cel\\u00e1 procedura nep\\u0159\\u00edjemn\\u00e1. Pokud m\\u00e1te i tak pot\\u0159ebu pou\\u017e\\u00edt tamponek, namo\\u010dte ho do vody a vym\\u00e1\\u010dkn\\u011bte z\\u00a0n\\u011bj p\\u0159ebyte\\u010dnou vodu. Ml\\u00e9ko dejte do dlan\\u011b, naneste na obli\\u010dej a krk a prov\\u00e1d\\u011bjte lehounkou mas\\u00e1\\u017e. Nabal\\u00ed se tak v\\u0161echny ne\\u010distoty a z\\u00e1rove\\