(38, '{\"title\":\"\\u010cistic\\u00ed ple\\u0165ov\\u00e9 tonikum\",\"id\":\"cistici-pletove-tonikum\",\"price\":\"370\",\"categories\":[],\"manufacturer\":\"naobay\",\"descriptionShort\":\"\",\"description\":\"<p>V tomto toniku je koncentrov\\u00e1na aktivn\\u00ed pumpa, kter\\u00e1 p\\u0159inese va\\u0161\\u00ed k\\u016f\\u017ei ve\\u0161ker\\u00fd p\\u016fvab.\\u00a0Obsahuje hydrolyzovan\\u00e9 b\\u00edlkoviny z r\\u00fd\\u017ee, malinov\\u00e9ho extraktu *, altea * a m\\u011bs\\u00ed\\u010dku, ani\\u017e byste zapomn\\u011bli na kv\\u011btinovou pomeran\\u010dovou vodu, kter\\u00e1 dod\\u00e1v\\u00e1 va\\u0161\\u00ed poko\\u017ece hebkost a sv\\u011b\\u017eest.<br \\/>Extrakt z malin\\u00edku * p\\u016fsob\\u00ed d\\u00edky obsahu vitaminu C jako antioxidant a proti voln\\u00fdm radik\\u00e1l\\u016fm. Altea * zklid\\u0148uje a chr\\u00e1n\\u00ed poko\\u017eku p\\u0159ed vn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00edmi agresemi a bojuje proti degradaci p\\u0159\\u00edrodn\\u00ed kyseliny hyaluronov\\u00e9 obsa\\u017een\\u00e9 v poko\\u017ece.\\u00a0Extrakt z m\\u011bs\\u00ed\\u010dku * hydratuje a zklid\\u0148uje poko\\u017eku.<\\/p><p><em>Jak pou\\u017e\\u00edvat<\\/em><br \\/>Aplikujte pomoc\\u00ed vatov\\u00e9ho tamponku, jemn\\u011b mas\\u00edrujte, aby se tonikum rovnom\\u011brn\\u011b rozprost\\u0159elo po poko\\u017ece.\\u00a0M\\u016f\\u017ee b\\u00fdt pou\\u017eit jako z\\u00e1v\\u011bre\\u010dn\\u00e1 f\\u00e1ze \\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed pleti, nebo s \\u00fapln\\u011b vy\\u010di\\u0161t\\u011bnou plet\\u00ed jako koktejl \\u00fa\\u010dinn\\u00fdch l\\u00e1tek.<br \\/><br \\/><em>Ingredience<\\/em><br \\/>Aqua,\\u00a0CITRUS AURANTIUM DULCIS FRUIT WATER*,\\u00a0Glycerin,\\u00a0Propanediol,\\u00a0Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Water*,\\u00a0Mentha Sativa Leaf Water*,\\u00a0Hydrolyzed Rice Protein,\\u00a0Rubus Idaeus Fruit Extract*,\\u00a0Helichrysum Stoechas Flower Extract*,\\u00a0Althaea officinalis Root Extract*,\\u00a0Calendula officinalis flower extract*,\\u00a0potass