 Gum, Parfum**.<\\/p><p><br \\/>*Suroviny z ekologick\\u00e9ho zem\\u011bd\\u011blstv\\u00ed<\\/p><p>**P\\u0159\\u00edrodn\\u00ed v\\u016fn\\u011b (z\\u00edskan\\u00e9 z esenci\\u00e1ln\\u00edch olej\\u016f)<\\/p>\",\"image\":{\"src\":\"Naobay\\/Cerna_maska_s_fosilnim_drevem.jpg\"},\"additionalImages\":[],\"variants\":[],\"specifications\":[{\"title\":\"mnozstvi\",\"value\":\"75 ml\"}],\"published\":\"1\",\"created\":\"2022-03-13 19:46:47\",\"stockStatus\":\"skladem\",\"usages\":[]}'),
